n the passage as addressing automated decision-making?','The second paragraph mentions that \"The European Union\'s General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), which includes provisions specifically addressing automated decision-making, exemplifies one approach to establishing guardrails for AI development while preserving individual privacy rights.\"'),(167,'2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000','What solution does the passage suggest for addressing algorithmic bias?','The third paragraph states that \"Addressing these concerns requires diverse development teams, careful dataset curation, regular algorithmic audits, and ongoing monitoring.\"'),(168,'2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000','What are the two main components of the immune system mentioned in the recording?','The immunologist states that \"The system has two main components: innate immunity and adaptive immunity.\"'),(169,'2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000','Which cells produce antibodies according to the recording?','According to the immunologist, \"B cells, which produce antibodies that tag invaders for destruction.\"'),(170,'2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000','What function do dendritic cells serve in the immune system?','The recording explains that \"Dendritic cells act as messengers, capturing pathogen information and presenting it to other immune cells.\"'),(171,'2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000','What does a share of stock represent according to the recording?','The financial analyst explains that \"When you buy a share of stock, you\'re purchasing a small piece of that company.\"'),(172,'2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 09:38:21.000000','What relationship do interest rates and bond prices have?','The recording states that \"Interest rates and bond prices have an inverse relationship – when interest rates rise, existi