ikTok has shifted communication from text-based to image and video-centric formats.\"'),(200,'2025-05-31 10:41:31.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 10:41:31.000000','How much time does the average person spend on social media daily?','The passage states \"Studies indicate that the average person spends over 2.5 hours daily on social media.\"'),(201,'2025-05-31 17:46:34.275870',_binary '','2025-05-31 17:46:34.275874','How has technology changed the way people communicate in recent years?','This question asks you to reflect on how advancements like smartphones, messaging apps, and social media have influenced human communication. You can mention both positive (e.g., faster, more global) and negative (e.g., less face-to-face interaction) effects'),(202,'2025-05-31 17:46:34.286943',_binary '','2025-05-31 17:46:34.286949','Do you think people rely too much on technology? Why or why not?','This question encourages critical thinking about modern society’s dependence on technology. You might mention areas like navigation, shopping, education, and the potential risks of over-reliance.'),(203,'2025-05-31 17:47:03.364742',_binary '','2025-05-31 17:47:03.364748',' What are the benefits of traveling to other countries?','This question invites you to talk about personal growth, learning new cultures, making international friends, or gaining new perspectives through travel.'),(204,'2025-05-31 17:47:03.376003',_binary '','2025-05-31 17:47:03.376006','How can traveling help people become more open-minded?',' This question focuses on how encountering different lifestyles, customs, and values can reduce prejudice and promote global understanding.'),(205,'2025-05-31 17:56:01.332697',_binary '','2025-05-31 17:56:01.332729','How has social media changed the way people interact with each other?','Focus on instant messaging, global connection, and digital relationships.'),(206,'2025-05-31 17:56:01.353193',_binary '','2025-05-31 17:56:01.353199','What are some of the negative effects of