ges are there in the sleep cycle?','The passage explains \"The sleep cycle consists of four stages: three non-REM stages and one REM stage.\"'),(216,'2025-05-31 11:00:17.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:00:17.000000','How many hours of sleep does the National Sleep Foundation recommend for adults aged 18-64?','The passage states \"The National Sleep Foundation recommends 7-9 hours of sleep per night for adults aged 18-64.\"'),(217,'2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000','According to the World Economic Forum, how many jobs could AI displace by 2025?','The passage states \"The World Economic Forum estimates that by 2025, AI could displace 85 million jobs globally.\"'),(218,'2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000','Which industries are expected to see job growth according to the passage?','The passage mentions \"Industries such as healthcare, education, and creative services are expected to see job growth.\"'),(219,'2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000','What is the reported benefit for companies investing in employee training?','The passage states \"Companies investing in employee training report 23% higher employee retention rates.\"'),(220,'2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000','How much plastic waste enters marine environments annually?','The passage states \"with an estimated 8 million tons of plastic waste entering marine environments annually.\"'),(221,'2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000','What size defines microplastics according to the passage?','The passage defines \"Microplastics, particles smaller than 5 millimeters.\"'),(222,'2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000',_binary '','2025-05-31 11:03:23.000000','According to the Ellen MacArthur Foundation, what could happen by 2050 without significant action?','The passage states \"The Ellen MacArthur Foundation estimates that without significant action, there could be 