,'Need clear career goals and achievement strategy. Low scores from vague aspirations or unrealistic plans.'),(439,'2025-06-11 11:50:00.667376',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:50:00.667387','Describe a professional skill you\'ve recently developed or are currently working on. Why is it important?','Need specific skill development and importance explanation. Low scores from no learning examples or unclear relevance.'),(440,'2025-06-11 11:50:00.678617',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:50:00.678626','How do you stay updated with trends and developments in your field of interest?\n','Need learning resources and knowledge application. Low scores from no updating methods or passive learning.'),(441,'2025-06-11 11:51:12.938357',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:51:12.938396','What current social or environmental issue concerns you most? Why do you think it\'s important to address?','Need specific issue and importance explanation. Low scores from general concerns or weak reasoning.'),(442,'2025-06-11 11:51:12.964401',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:51:12.964412','How has technology changed the way people communicate? Do you think these changes are mostly positive or negative?\n',' Need technology impact analysis and clear position. Low scores from superficial observations or no stance.'),(443,'2025-06-11 11:51:12.979981',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:51:12.979995','Discuss the role of education in society. What changes would you make to improve the education system?\n','Need education analysis and improvement suggestions. Low scores from basic understanding or unrealistic changes.'),(444,'2025-06-11 11:52:04.366309',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:52:04.366338','What does success mean to you? How has your definition of success changed over time?','Need personal success definition and evolution. Low scores from cliché answers or no personal growth.\n'),(445,'2025-06-11 11:52:04.407427',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:52:04.407431','Do you believe that people can truly change their fundamental personality traits? Explain your reasoning.','Need philosophical position with supporting arguments. Low scores from simple yes/no or weak reasoning.'),(446,'2025-06-11 11:52:04.414845',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:52:04.414849','Discuss the importance of maintaining traditions versus embracing change. How do you balance these in your own life?\n','Need balance analysis and personal application. Low scores from one-sided view or no personal examples.'),(447,'2025-06-11 11:53:04.136526',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:53:04.136566','If you could solve one global problem, what would it be and what approach would you take?\n','Need specific global issue and realistic solution approach. Low scores from vague problems or impractical solutions.'),(448,'2025-06-11 11:53:04.162247',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:53:04.162261','Discuss the advantages and disadvantages of globalization. How has it affected your country or community?\n','Need balanced globalization analysis with local examples. Low scores from one-sided view or no local connection.'),(449,'2025-06-11 11:53:04.176692',_binary '','2025-06-11 11:53:04.176702','What role should government play in people\'s daily lives? Where do you think the balance should be between individual freedom and collective responsibility?','Need government role analysis and freedom-responsibility balance. Low scores from extreme positions or no personal reflection.'),(450,'2025-06-11 12:15:08.518541',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:15:08.518598','What are your favorite foods? Describe the foods you enjoy eating most and explain why you like them.','In this question, you should talk about 2-3 foods you really enjoy. For each food, explain why you like it (taste, memories, health benefits, etc.). Use simple descriptive words like \"delicious,\" \"sweet,\" \"spicy,\" or \"healthy.\" You can also mention when or where you usually eat these foods.'),(451,'2025-06-11 12:15:08.551995',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:15:08.552004','Can you cook? Tell me about your cooking experience. What dishes can you make, or what would you like to learn to cook?','If you can cook, describe what dishes you know how to make and how you learned (from family, friends, online, etc.). If you cannot cook, talk about what you would like to learn and why. Use simple past tense to talk about your experience and \"would like to\" for future plans.'),(452,'2025-06-11 12:15:08.561376',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:15:08.561381','Describe a typical meal in your country. What do people usually eat for breakfast, lunch, and dinner?','Talk about common foods in your country for each meal time. Use present simple tense (\"People usually eat...\") and describe the main ingredients or dishes. You can also mention if meal times are different from other countries or any special eating customs.'),(453,'2025-06-11 12:16:00.663978',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:16:00.663990','Describe your hometown or city. What is it like? What are some interesting places there?','Talk about the basic features of your hometown (size, location, weather). Mention 2-3 interesting places like parks, museums, markets, or famous buildings. Use descriptive adjectives like \"big,\" \"small,\" \"beautiful,\" \"busy,\" or \"quiet.\" Explain why these places are special or what people do there.'),(454,'2025-06-11 12:16:00.694375',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:16:00.694390','Have you ever traveled to another city or country? Tell me about a trip you took or a place you would like to visit.','If you have traveled, use past tense to describe where you went, what you did, and what you liked about the trip. If you haven\'t traveled much, talk about a place you want to visit using \"I would like to...\" or \"I want to...\" and explain why this place interests you.'),(455,'2025-06-11 12:16:00.726784',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:16:00.726790','What do you think makes a place interesting to visit? What kinds of attractions or activities do you enjoy when traveling?','Give your opinion about what makes places worth visiting (beautiful nature, historical sites, good food, friendly people, etc.). Talk about activities you enjoy or would enjoy (sightseeing, trying local food, shopping, taking photos). Use phrases like \"I think...\" or \"In my opinion...\" to express your ideas.'),(456,'2025-06-11 12:28:48.537672',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:28:48.537703','Tell me about yourself. What\'s your name, where are you from, and what do you do?','Give a basic introduction including your name, age (if you want), where you live or where you\'re from, and your occupation (student, worker, etc.). Use simple present tense like \"I am...\" or \"I come from...\" Keep it natural and friendly, like meeting someone new.'),(457,'2025-06-11 12:28:48.577729',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:28:48.577733','Describe your typical daily routine from morning to evening. What time do you wake up and what activities do you do?','Talk about your regular daily activities in order from morning to night. Use time expressions like \"at 7 AM,\" \"in the morning,\" \"after lunch.\" Use present simple tense for habits (\"I wake up,\" \"I go to,\" \"I have\"). Mention 5-6 main activities throughout your day.'),(458,'2025-06-11 12:28:48.588550',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:28:48.588554','What are your hobbies and interests? Why do you enjoy these activities?','Describe 2-3 activities you like to do in your free time. Explain why you enjoy them using phrases like \"I like it because...\" or \"It makes me feel...\" You can talk about sports, reading, music, games, or any activities you find fun or relaxing.'),(459,'2025-06-11 12:29:36.689689',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:29:36.689747','Describe your family. How many people are in your family and what are they like?','Talk about your family members (parents, siblings, etc.) and give basic information about each person (age, job, personality). Use descriptive adjectives like \"kind,\" \"funny,\" \"hardworking,\" or \"friendly.\" You can also mention family activities you do together.'),(460,'2025-06-11 12:29:36.714755',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:29:36.714762','Tell me about your best friend. How did you meet and what do you like to do together?','Describe one close friend, including how you met them (at school, work, neighborhood) and what makes them special. Talk about activities you enjoy doing together using present simple tense. Explain why you are good friends using phrases like \"We both like...\" or \"He/she is very...\"'),(461,'2025-06-11 12:29:36.734799',_binary '','2025-06-11 12:29:36.734810','What makes a good friend? What qualities are important in friendship?','Give your opinion about the characteristics of a good friend. Use adjectives like \"honest,\" \"loyal,\" \"supportive,\" or \"trustworthy.\" Explain why these qualities matter using phrases like \"I think...\" or \"A good friend should...\" You can give examples of good friendship behaviors.'),(462,'2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000',_binary '','2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000','Where is Anna going on Saturday morning?','Anna says \"on Saturday morning I\'m going to visit my grandmother.\"'),(463,'2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000',_binary '','2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000','What time is Mike\'s soccer game?','Mike states \"I have a soccer game at 2:00 PM on Saturday.\"'),(464,'2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000',_binary '','2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000','What type of game is Mike playing?','Mike explains \"it\'s the final match of our school tournament.\"'),(465,'2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000',_binary '','2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000','What time should Anna come to the barbecue?','Mike says \"Around 1:00 PM would be perfect.\"'),(466,'2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000',_binary '','2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000','What will Anna bring to the party?','Anna says \"I\'ll bring some homemade cookies.\"'),(467,'2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000',_binary '','2025-06-11 05:43:11.000000','What is David\'s presentation about?','David clearly states \"Today I want to share some simple ways we can help protect our planet.\"'),(468,'2025-0