INSERT INTO `submit_test` (`id`, `created_at`, `status`, `updated_at`, `comment`, `score`, `test_id`, `user_id`) VALUES (1,'2025-05-17 13:17:51.890778',_binary '\0','2025-05-17 13:17:51.890789','',0,3,6),(2,'2025-06-01 15:55:20.943951',_binary '\0','2025-06-01 15:55:20.943964','',0,12,5),(3,'2025-06-03 14:44:25.141265',_binary '','2025-06-03 14:44:42.263281','Your reading responses demonstrate strong literal comprehension, accurately summarizing key details. However, your inference skills need refinement—you often miss subtle thematic connections between paragraphs. To improve, practice annotating texts to identify implicit linkages, then write 2-sentence explanations justifying your interpretations. This will deepen your analytical engagement with subtext.',25,1,5),(4,'2025-06-03 21:20:19.250477',_binary '','2025-06-03 21:22:49.563703','Excellent work! Your vocabulary shows depth and your grammar fundamentals are solid. Focus on complex sentence structures to elevate your writing further.',40,14,5),(5,'2025-06-03 21:37:23.783402',_binary '','2025-06-03 21:38:02.661729','Your writing demonstrates strong idea development with clear, logical progression in arguments. However, transitions between ideas can feel abrupt, disrupting flow. To improve, practice using transitional phrases like \'furthermore\' or \'conversely\' to link paragraphs. Try rewriting one paragraph with explicit transitions to enhance coherence.',0,15,10),(6,'2025-06-03 21:38:49.959815',_binary '','2025-06-03 21:41:48.407438','Your writing demonstrates strong idea development with clear, logical progression in each paragraph. However, transitions between sections occasionally feel abrupt, disrupting the overall flow. Focus on using transitional phrases like \'consequently\' or \'in contrast\' to enhance cohesion. Practice rewriting your section endings to explicitly link to the next paragraph\'s topic.',85,15,10),(7,'2025-06-03 23:43:48.113782',_binary '','2025-06-03 23:44:37.856081','Your auditory discrimination is strong, as evidenced by accurate identification of key details in fast-paced dialogues. However, context interpretation needs refinement—you missed subtle cues in inferential questions. To improve, practice with advanced podcasts, pausing to predict speaker intentions before hearing options.',46,16,10),(8,'2025-06-04 08:47:02.359205',_binary '','2025-06-04 08:47:35.490505','Your comprehension demonstrates strong inference skills, evidenced by your ability to deduce nuanced themes from subtle textual clues. However, you occasionally miss implicit connections between key ideas. To deepen analysis, practice annotating passages by explicitly labeling inferred relationships (e.g., \'A contrasts B because...\') to strengthen implicit linkage recognition.',40,14,10),(9,'2025-06-04 09:30:49.045634',_binary '','2025-06-04 09:31:22.591322','Your reading responses show strong literal comprehension, accurately summarizing key details from passages. However, you often miss implicit connections—like inferring a character\'s motive from contextual clues. To improve, practice \'reading between the lines\' by annotating texts with hypotheses about unstated themes or relationships before verifying with evidence.',53,14,10),(10,'2025-06-04 09:31:31.887240',_binary '\0','2025-06-04 09:31:31.887250','',0,14,10),(11,'2025-06-11 21:43:43.699039',_binary '','2025-06-11 21:58:39.247344','Your vocabulary demonstrates strong command of academic and corporate terms (e.g., \'campaign,\' \'contribution\'). Grammar analysis reveals consistent errors in auxiliary verb usage (\'leave\' vs \'leaves,\' \'has eaten\' vs \'had been eaten\'). Target irregular verb tenses by practicing past participle forms systematically. Record yourself narrating daily routines to reinforce correct tense usage.',59,7,5),(12,'2025-06-11 21:59:22.303638',_binary '\0','2025-06-11 21:59:22.303638','',0,7,5);
